---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Construction Site Log & Daily Report Software | BuildWorkPro" description="Digital daily site logs for construction. Record weather, crew hours, equipment, materials, and notes from the field. Replace paper logs.">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Features</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
          Construction Site Log Software
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Replace paper daily logs with digital field documentation. Record weather conditions, crew hours, equipment usage, materials delivered, and work performed -- all searchable, all exportable, all tied to the project.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <!-- TODO: Restore "Start free trial" button at launch -->
          <span class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-slate-400 rounded-xl cursor-default">
            Coming Soon
          </span>
          <a href="/features/" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-slate-700 bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl transition-all">
            All features
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overview -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20">
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate mx-auto">
        <h2>Build an airtight record of every jobsite day</h2>
        <p>
          Daily site logs are your first line of defense in disputes, delay claims, and payment disagreements. When a GC says your crew was not on site, a timestamped digital log with weather data, personnel counts, and work descriptions tells a different story. BuildWorkPro makes it fast for your foremen to log the day and easy for your office to review and archive it.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every site log is tied to a specific project and date. Over the course of a job, your logs become a complete daily history of what happened, who was there, and what conditions were like. Search by date range, project, or keyword to find exactly what you need when you need it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Capabilities -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center mb-12">Key capabilities</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-cyan-50 ring-1 ring-cyan-100 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Daily log entries</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Create a log for each project and date. Structured fields ensure consistent documentation -- your foremen fill in the same data every day without missing anything.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-cyan-50 ring-1 ring-cyan-100 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15a4.5 4.5 0 004.5 4.5H18a3.75 3.75 0 001.332-7.257 3 3 0 00-3.758-3.848 5.25 5.25 0 00-10.233 2.33A4.502 4.502 0 002.25 15z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Weather tracking</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Record temperature, conditions, and weather impacts for every day on site. Weather records are critical for delay claims and schedule impact documentation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-cyan-50 ring-1 ring-cyan-100 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 002.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 004.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 00-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 018.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Crew and personnel</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Log the number of workers on site by trade, classification, and hours worked. Build a daily manpower record that supports your pay applications and labor claims.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-cyan-50 ring-1 ring-cyan-100 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17l-5.384 3.079A1.243 1.243 0 014.5 17.1V6.9a1.243 1.243 0 011.536-1.149l5.384 3.079m0 0l5.384-3.079A1.243 1.243 0 0118.34 6.9V17.1a1.243 1.243 0 01-1.536 1.149L11.42 15.17z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Equipment and materials</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Record equipment used and materials received on site each day. Track deliveries, equipment hours, and material consumption against your project budget.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-cyan-50 ring-1 ring-cyan-100 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.827 6.175A2.31 2.31 0 015.186 7.23c-.38.054-.757.112-1.134.175C2.999 7.58 2.25 8.507 2.25 9.574V18a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h15A2.25 2.25 0 0021.75 18V9.574c0-1.067-.75-1.994-1.802-2.169a47.865 47.865 0 00-1.134-.175 2.31 2.31 0 01-1.64-1.055l-.822-1.316a2.192 2.192 0 00-1.736-1.039 48.774 48.774 0 00-5.232 0 2.192 2.192 0 00-1.736 1.039l-.821 1.316z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 12.75a4.5 4.5 0 11-9 0 4.5 4.5 0 019 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Photo attachments</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Attach photos directly to any site log entry. Document progress, conditions, safety issues, or completed work with visual evidence tied to the date and project.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white">
          <div class="inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-cyan-50 ring-1 ring-cyan-100 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 16.5v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75V16.5M16.5 12L12 16.5m0 0L7.5 12m4.5 4.5V3" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Export to PDF</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Generate PDF reports of your daily logs for archival, sharing with GCs, or submitting as backup documentation with pay apps and delay claims.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <!-- TODO: Restore "Ready to get started?" CTA with trial button at launch -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Coming Soon</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 mb-8">We're preparing for launch. Internal testing in progress.</p>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-slate-400 rounded-xl cursor-default">
        Coming Soon
      </span>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
